00:00:03,410 --> 00:00:07,650
If it's my right to kill him, then it's my right to let him go.

2
00:00:07,650 --> 00:00:13,730
But let it be said, me letting him go does not make me a merciful coward.

3
00:00:13,730 --> 00:00:17,649
I'll go by Pietro's side on all future missions.

4
00:00:17,649 --> 00:00:27,410
That's so sweet.

5
00:00:27,410 --> 00:00:30,929
Maybe I can do something to delay the completion by joining this mission.

6
00:00:30,929 --> 00:00:42,079
Then the marriage will be annulled smoothly.

7
00:00:42,079 --> 00:00:45,859
Yeah, what are we doing here? Mission's not done yet.

8
00:00:45,859 --> 00:00:51,570
Well, the black wedding is our formal night.

9
00:00:51,570 --> 00:00:54,179
And you need a new suit for the occasion.

10
00:00:54,179 --> 00:00:59,020
Yeah, isn't it a bit early for all this? Mission's not over yet.

11
00:00:59,020 --> 00:01:03,869
Early. I actually can't wait to take your clothes off on one.

12
00:01:03,869 --> 00:01:05,870
I'm not your pet, Pietro.

13
00:01:05,870 --> 00:01:31,870
But I'll take you to the real destination.

14
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:34,370
Okay. Let's go.

